\section{Materials}

\begin{frame}{Images}
Raster images from Copernicus were cropped to the interested areas and downloaded
\begin{itemize}
    \item 4 tiff images for the FCOVER, from year 2020 to 2023
    \item 4 tiff images for the NDVI index, from year 2020 to 2023
\end{itemize}
The images chosen cover the months of April, May or June, so between the spring and summer period. 
\end{frame}


